{
  "3257730": {
    "name": "SkullLord 骸骷王",
    "steam_appid": 3257730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事剧情以异世界转生者得到了全新的意识后突然被召唤到某大陆上开始展开...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主角是一具骸骨可以分配特质属性点数.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看个人喜好分配.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/20d262f0b6ff817f40a8697c63ebe471.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=574 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/20d262f0b6ff817f40a8697c63ebe471.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/20d262f0b6ff817f40a8697c63ebe471.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些额外属性会在原有的基础属性上再次提升能力(主要体现在战斗场景中)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >力量提升物理攻击力, 全能提升法术攻击力, 耐久提高防御力, 幸运代表暴击.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原罪是一项非常有意思的设定, 在游戏城镇中会有npc, 玩家如果感染传染病(如果你喝了不干净的水)后和npc交谈会有几率传染给npc, npc得病后会消失, 需要一定时间才会再次刷新, 原罪会增加, 这个数值会影响骸骨兵的额外攻击伤害.此外击败人族敌人都会累计原罪.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中会有体力条, 行走期间会消耗体力条(可以通过饮水和药剂补充体力条)当体力条过低会造成行走缓慢.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/6908775d12e813e1cb7cefd1676e66ff.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/6908775d12e813e1cb7cefd1676e66ff.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/6908775d12e813e1cb7cefd1676e66ff.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当玩家由于各种原因死亡, 会被扔到离你最近的复活点(通常会是离你最近的城镇旅馆地下)并不会游戏结束.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你进入城镇就会自动设定当前城镇为复活点.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中可以通过任务获得各种不同性格不同战斗方式的女性角色为你作战.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有昼夜交替, 会有不同的任务线npc和魔物出现在不同的时间段.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主线任务会有一位女性npc引导开启(按键盘T键可以随时召唤她)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/5d5ddd613408fe167b321cb702b3edce.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=572 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/5d5ddd613408fe167b321cb702b3edce.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/5d5ddd613408fe167b321cb702b3edce.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骸骨通过任务可以获得不同的形象皮肤. 有些皮肤会有特殊效果, 通过形态接受特殊任务或者某个势力的任务线.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个城镇会有不同的性质.比如新手村是被教会控制, 你必须换上某个皮肤才能安全进入, 有些贸易型的都市就可以自由出入不受影响.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/63614282c0953e5fc1a90c7bc16c4e0c.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/63614282c0953e5fc1a90c7bc16c4e0c.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/63614282c0953e5fc1a90c7bc16c4e0c.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中可以使用QTE战斗模式(难度较大)你也可以关闭QTE战斗模式采用普通模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/7f078b4fa2d73fe1943132ca9d06d285.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=574 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/7f078b4fa2d73fe1943132ca9d06d285.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/7f078b4fa2d73fe1943132ca9d06d285.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以挑战难度较大的QTE战斗模式 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此战斗模式在技能释放中会有按键提示和独特的战斗特效</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/8c2b88f381211b6e529aac0703e46dc4.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=582 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/8c2b88f381211b6e529aac0703e46dc4.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/8c2b88f381211b6e529aac0703e46dc4.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光源系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以调整场景中的色调和泛光效果(按键盘B键可以呼出和关闭光源设置菜单)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弓箭系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各类弓箭有不同属性和入手方法, 可以通过魔物掉落入手或者合成制作, 每次远程攻击会消耗弓箭数量, 弓箭的选择可以在箭矢菜单中选择也可以在战斗中切换. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的武器防具可以在菜单中合成(需要获得各种必要素材)可以在商店购买或者击败魔物和完成相关任务获得</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合成制作出的武器防具更强大！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >缝合怪系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >封印魔物和人类NPC可以进行合成.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次封印的魔物会有不同的天赋词条和技能(魔物可以在菜单魔物皿中查看, 如果不喜欢可以分解出素材)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些稀有特殊技能只有缝合出的魔物才会拥有.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天赋词条会有正向有利的增益, 降低能力的负面, 两面性的双刃剑四种和稀有强大的传说.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有几率刷出的更强大的生物为你出战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/223bf4fef11e38cd55297fb2fc46f194.poster.avif?t=1769192733\" width=574 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/223bf4fef11e38cd55297fb2fc46f194.webm?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/223bf4fef11e38cd55297fb2fc46f194.mp4?t=1769192733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras/0386967cf9a0df9459a8ebae68a7cf70.avif?t=1769192733\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257730/extras_big/0386967cf9a0df9459a8ebae68a7cf70.avif?t=1769192733 width=800 height=533 /></span></p>",
